examples.en: My watch is a perfect goer.

She went a long way to see him.

examples.en: She went downstairs to the kitchen.

examples.en: She goes to the office every morning and comes home in the evening.
examples.ru: Каждое утро она уходит на работу, а вечером приходит домой.
